data.title: Run with Team Lifeline Bondi at City to Surf 2024
data.meta_description: Join Team Lifeline Bondi in the 2024 City2Surf this August! The first 100 people to join Team Lifeline Bondi will receive a FREE running shirt, thanks to our generous sponsor, Bondi Bowlo.
data.text:
Are you running the City to Surf this year?

Join Team Lifeline Bondi in the City2Surf this August and help us save lives.

The first 100 participants to join Team Bondi will snag a FREE running shirt thanks to Bondi Bowling Club.

You can also choose to fundraise to make an even bigger impact! Together, we can ensure that if you, or someone you know is ever feeling overwhelmed, 13 11 14 will be available for you to get free and confidential support.
